[BORDERLESS TRIPS - TRAVEL SPONSORSHIP / INVITATION LETTER TEMPLATE]

Date: [Insert Date]

To,
The Visa Officer,
[Embassy/Consulate Name of Destination Country, e.g., Embassy of France]
[Embassy Address, e.g., London, United Kingdom]

Subject: Letter of Sponsorship / Invitation for [Name of Applicant]

Respected Visa Officer,

I, [Name of Sponsor], residing at [Sponsor's Full Address in Destination/Host Country or UK], holding [Sponsor's Nationality / Residency Status, e.g., British Passport No. XXXXXX], write this letter to confirm my sponsorship and invitation of [Name of Applicant] (Passport No. [Applicant Passport No.]), who resides at [Applicant UK Address].

The applicant is my [Relationship, e.g., Friend / Sister / Husband / Colleague] and wishes to visit me in [Destination Country] from [Start Date] to [End Date] for [Purpose, e.g., Tourism / Family Visit].

During the applicant's stay in [Destination Country], they will be residing at my property located at [Full Address of Accommodation]. 

Furthermore, I confirm that:
[Option A: Full Financial Sponsorship]
- I will cover all expenses of the applicant's trip, including return flights, accommodation, medical insurance, daily living expenses, and repatriation costs.
- Attached, please find my proof of income, last 3 months bank statements, and employment verification.

[Option B: Accommodation Sponsorship Only]
- I will be providing accommodation and lodging for the applicant at my address. The applicant will cover their own travel and daily living expenses.

Attached to this letter are the following supporting documents:
1. Certified copy of my passport / residence permit.
2. Proof of accommodation (utility bill / rent agreement / official host certificate).
3. Last 3 months bank statements (if Option A is selected).
4. Letter of employment (if Option A is selected).

Please do not hesitate to contact me if you require any further information.

Yours sincerely,

[Signature of Sponsor]

----------------------------------
Name: [Sponsor's Printed Name]
Phone: [Sponsor's Phone Number]
Email: [Sponsor's Email Address]
